<para>
  When <command>Long_Layer_Names</command> is <emphasis>on</emphasis>,
  the <link linkend="Section-Graphics-LayerList">Layer List</link> in
  the <link linkend="Chapter-Graphics">Graphics</link> window shows
  the full set of parameters for each &layer;.  Often this is too much
  information.  When <command>Long_Layer_Names</command> is
  <emphasis>off</emphasis>, only the displayed object and <xref
  linkend="RegisteredClass-DisplayMethod"/> are shown, with
  abbreviated arguments.
</para>


